  "query": "Now I want you to do a deep exploration of unimatrix.  I want you to understand all of the features/capabilties it has.  We've built this from the perspective of a focused domain, but have always wanted the core to be domain agnostic.  What I want to know, is just how far away we are from this platform being domain agnostic (meaning, being applicable to other data domains, things maybe not even workflow centric)... Is there a way to register a different set of 'categories', is the workflow deeply wound into the solution... and are the weights we've adjusted recently are too heavily scoped to a agentic development tool.  Write this research in product/research/ass-022.  Be thorough, then continue and theorize different use cases for this type of platform... I see this platform similar to github.com/ruvnet/ruvector.  Be innovative in thinking about how it could be used to for air quality environmental pattern matching github.com/dug-21/neural-data-platform or other novel use cases.  This is a large request... break it down and iterate... this does not follow most of our existing protocols, as it is research only",
